Be the Player You Were Meant To Be

The X1 basketball shoe lets your feet move naturally, giving you access to your full range of motion and strength. The X1 also gives you feedback from the court, so you can move with precision, control, and explosive power.
Maximizing your performance isn’t about working harder. It’s about moving better. Transform your game in the groundbreaking X1.
Gives you more energy for your sprints, cuts, and jumps.
Provide more feedback from the court, giving your brain more information for reaction and coordination.
Data from thousands of 3D foot scans were used to create a barefoot basketball shoe that matches the unique anatomy of a woman’s foot.
Low stack height and zero-drop heel let you move with explosive force and graceful agility.
Join the Revolution
The X1 doesn’t just challenge limits — it shatters them.

Join the barefoot revolution and take your game to a new level of play. Our Xero Shoes partners and professional trainers show you how to go from conventional shoes that constrain your feet to barefoot shoes that put you in control of your game.
